data.description: 3 bedroom single family home PLUS 2 other buildings! This is truly a unique property. Conveniently located on State Highway 94 but set back from road and secluded by row of tall bushes.  Appx. 1,200SF commercial building is close to Route 94 with parking and is currently leased. Behind main house is another building that has an appx. 425SF room that could be used as an office or potentially be converted to a studio apartment (must check with Zoning). Lower level of rear building is appx. 2,000SF with concrete floor and was most recently used as a kennel. Large fenced in front yard.
